author: 444.linaa
description: Hello, my name is Alina Valenzuela and in febuary 2025 I fell sick with the flu.. I am doing much better and made a full recovery but I thought I should should take a moment to share my story. On February 4th, 2025 I began to feel pains in my chest and wasn‚Äôt sure why. My mom rushed me to the ER as the pains got worse and worse. No one could figure out what was so they kept me for several days to do testing. Little by little the doctors finally figured out what was going on and later decided to transfer me to a bigger hospital. As they were getting ready to transfer me I went into cardiac arrest which was the scariest thing for my family and friends. After they got me stable they where able to transfer me as quickly as possible to Texas children‚Äôs hospital in Houston Texas. After many many surgeries and being in a coma for 2 weeks I finally started to wake up. A few weeks later I was transferred to a rehab unit and made a full recovery! My overall goal was to walk again to be able to walk the stage at graduation! Now that I have reached that goal I am  forever proud of myself and couldn‚Äôt do it without the support of my family friends and my wonderful boyfriendüíû #fyp„Ç∑ #viral #survivor #texaschildrenshospital #flu
